Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.41,RogerMonologue,,0,0,0,,os sonhos da humanidade e a vontade herdada..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.52,RogerMonologue,,0,0,0,,Enquanto as pessoas buscarem a liberdade,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:26.15,RogerMonologue,,0,0,0,,essas coisas nunca deixarão de existir.
